title: Ep. 434: Another Marvel Character is DOA
itunes:title: Another Marvel Character is DOA
description: In this episode of For Canon Sake, we talk about the upcoming Kraven the Hunter in Sony's SPider-Man universe. We also discuss how even the leftists hate Miles Morales' Thor.
